[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":257},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200928\u002F777542166\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200928\u002F777542166\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200928\u002F777542166\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200928\u002F777542166\u002F":234,"related:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200928\u002F777542166\u002F":243},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F28\u002Flearn-hexo-15-vexo-theme\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":216,"date":217,"description":18,"extension":218,"lang":219,"meta":220,"navigation":221,"path":222,"readingMinutes":223,"seo":224,"standalone":225,"stem":226,"tags":227,"tldr":231,"updated":231,"url":232,"__hash__":233},"content\u002F試著學 Hexo\u002F15-試著學-Hexo-主題篇-Vexo-主題.md","(15) 試著學 Hexo - 主題篇 - Vexo 主題","777542166",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":210},"minimark",[11,15,19,22,25,28,45,60,67,70,74,81,107,110,116,122,129,135,138,144,157,177,180,185,192,203,206],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"接下來讓我們嘗試安裝另一個主題吧！",[12,20,21],{"id":21},"下載主題",[16,23,24],{},"接下來要安裝的主題是 Vexo，它是基於 Vue.js 官方文件所啟發的主題，如果你相當喜歡 Vue.js 的風格那麼就不能錯過。",[16,26,27],{},"下載方式與前面相同，在終端機輸入以下指令",[29,30,35],"pre",{"className":31,"code":32,"language":33,"meta":34,"style":34},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","git clone https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fyanm1ng\u002Fhexo-theme-vexo.git themes\u002Fvexo\n","cmd","",[36,37,38],"code",{"__ignoreMap":34},[39,40,43],"span",{"class":41,"line":42},"line",1,[39,44,32],{},[16,46,47,48,51,52,55,56,59],{},"接下來就可以看 themes 資料夾底下看到 vexo 的主題資料夾，在這邊與前一篇完全相同，然後打開 ",[36,49,50],{},"hexo\u002F_config.yml"," 將剛剛的 ",[36,53,54],{},"theme: hueman"," 修改成 ",[36,57,58],{},"theme: vexo","，然後啟動模擬伺服器就可以看到主題替換成功囉",[16,61,62],{},[63,64],"img",{"alt":65,"src":66},"vexo","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-16%2016.56.08.png",[16,68,69],{},"是不是超級簡單?基本上絕大部分主題都是這樣子。",[12,71,73],{"id":72},"vexo-設置檔案","Vexo 設置檔案",[16,75,76,77,80],{},"基本上 Vexo 也是一個非常輕量的主題，因此在 ",[36,78,79],{},"theme\u002F_config.yml"," 可以讓新手不帶恐懼的入門，主要你會比較需要改的地方有幾個區塊",[82,83,84,97,102],"ul",{},[85,86,87,90,91,90,94],"li",{},[36,88,89],{},"author","、",[36,92,93],{},"description",[36,95,96],{},"keyword",[85,98,99],{},[36,100,101],{},"gitment config",[85,103,104],{},[36,105,106],{},"about",[16,108,109],{},"這三大區塊我會建議你調整一下，尤其是作者那區塊，而 gitment 你可以斟酌要使用 gitment 還是 disqus，只是要改一下相關 id 就是了。",[16,111,112,113],{},"接下來在畫面上的 Tags 與 Project 頁面你會發現點下去會出現錯誤，唯獨 about 頁面是正常的，這部分是因為我們並沒有建立這些頁面的關係而 about 是我們前面已經有建立的關係，但是在 Vexo 底下其實已經幫你準備好該頁面讓你不用在輸入 ",[36,114,115],{},"hexo new pages",[16,117,118],{},[63,119],{"alt":120,"src":121},"_source","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-16%2017.17.04.png",[16,123,124,125,128],{},"因此你只需要將 _source 底下的 Tags 與 Project 資料夾複製或是移動到 ",[36,126,127],{},"source"," 資料夾即可",[16,130,131],{},[63,132],{"alt":133,"src":134},"新增頁面","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-16%2017.19.25.png",[16,136,137],{},"接下重新啟動模擬伺服器，再去點 Tags 與 Project 就可以發現可以正常進入囉",[16,139,140],{},[63,141],{"alt":142,"src":143},"Project","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-16%2017.20.35.png",[16,145,146,147,149,150,152,153,156],{},"這時候你應該會說「Project 頁面怎麼會是別人的 GitHub，我可以改成自己的嗎？」，當然可以，你只需要打開 ",[36,148,79],{}," 並調整 ",[36,151,106],{}," 中的 ",[36,154,155],{},"github_username"," 即可，以我自己來舉例就是改成下方這樣",[29,158,162],{"className":159,"code":160,"language":161,"meta":34,"style":34},"language-yml shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","github_username: hsiangfeng\n","yml",[36,163,164],{"__ignoreMap":34},[39,165,166,169,173],{"class":41,"line":42},[39,167,155],{"class":168},"sKpQp",[39,170,172],{"class":171},"sMAXC",": ",[39,174,176],{"class":175},"sTRMh","hsiangfeng\n",[16,178,179],{},"此時重新啟動模擬伺服器就可以看到 Project 頁面變囉",[16,181,182],{},[63,183],{"alt":142,"src":184},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-16%2017.24.21.png",[16,186,187,188,191],{},"Vexo 非常的簡潔，但是唯一的缺點就是沒有支援多國語系，因此如果你想將簡體字修改成繁體字的話，就必須到 ",[36,189,190],{},"theme\u002Flayout"," 底下修改模板。",[16,193,194,195,202],{},"而這邊代表的使用人物是 PJCHENder 的 ",[196,197,201],"a",{"href":198,"rel":199},"https:\u002F\u002Fpjchender.github.io\u002F",[200],"nofollow","PJCHENder 未整理筆記","，你可以先逛過之後再決定是否要使用該主題哩~",[16,204,205],{},"那麼我們下一篇主題見~",[207,208,209],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}",{"title":34,"searchDepth":211,"depth":211,"links":212},2,[213,214,215],{"id":14,"depth":211,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":211,"text":21},{"id":72,"depth":211,"text":73},"Hexo","2020-09-28 00:00:01","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fhexo\u002F15-hexo-vexo","2",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"試著學 Hexo\u002F15-試著學-Hexo-主題篇-Vexo-主題",[216,228,229,230],"試著學 Hexo","第 12 屆 iT邦幫忙鐵人賽","Vexo",null,"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200928\u002F777542166\u002F","nPj6WZvyw7aNij9cwOaYdrZQ1eTjSewc9aFpkdsfwqk",{"newer":235,"older":2